org.icepdf.ri.common

Class KeyEventConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.icepdf.ri.common.KeyEventConstants

  • public class KeyEventConstants
extends Object
    The KeyEvent Class contains the key event and input event used for menu and button manipulatin via the keyboard. This class may need to be changed depending on region and languages.
